<div class=\"contributions\">\n            <p><strong>Donate Laptops:</strong> If you have a laptop that you no longer need, consider donating it to Laptop for All. Your old device could be the key to unlocking a world of opportunities for a deserving student.</p>\n            <p><strong>Financial Contributions:</strong> Your financial support allows us to purchase new laptops, upgrade existing ones, and cover operational costs. Every contribution, no matter how small, makes a significant difference.</p>\n            <p><strong>Spread the Word:</strong> Help us reach more students and potential donors by spreading the word about Laptop for All. Follow us on social media, share our mission, and let others know how they can contribute to creating a more inclusive future.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <a href=\"your_apply_now_link_here\" class=\"apply-button\">Apply Now</a>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"team-members\">\n        <h2>Our Team - Wordsmiths</h2>\n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <th>Name</th>\n                <th>Email</th>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Muhammad Hammad</td>\n                <td>hammadansari234@gmail.com</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Ubaidurrehman</td>\n                <td>iubaidrmn@gmail.com</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Zunaira Ashraf</td>\n                <td>ashrafzunaira7@gmail.com</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Manal Rani</td>\n                <td>fa21bscs0024@maju.edu.pk</td>\n            </tr>\n            <tr>\n                <td>Amina Ibrahim</td>\n                <td>aminabookreviews@gmail.com</td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n    </section>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n\n<!-- /wp:html -->', 'About us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '13-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-02-18 09:47:59', '2024-02-18 09:47:59', '', 13, 'http://wordsmith.42web.io/?p=129', 0, 'revision', '', 0